<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/tim-bestwick> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Tim Bestwick was appointed UKAEA’s Interim Chief Executive Officer in July 2025. Career highlights include: Chief Development Officer and Deputy CEO, UKAEA Chief Technology Officer and Director of Strategy, Communications & Business Development, UKAEA Executive Director, Business & Innovation at the Science & Technology Facilities Council. Non-Executive Director of the Harwell Science & Innovation Campus. Chair of the Eureka Network (the world’s largest international business to business innovation network). Non-Executive Director of ten start-up technology companies. ‘Innovation Sector Champion’ Award from AIRTO - the membership body for organisations operating in the UK’s innovation, research and technology sector. Chair of The Space Partnership Board"@en .
